&lt;h1 id="is-it-worth-being-wise"&gt;Is It Worth Being Wise?&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;February 2007&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A few days ago I finally figured out something I&amp;rsquo;ve wondered about for 25 years: the relationship between wisdom and intelligence. Anyone can see they&amp;rsquo;re not the same by the number of people who are smart, but not very wise. And yet intelligence and wisdom do seem related. How?&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>